    <p style="color: #d8e476; font-size: 28px; font-family: orgonboldregular; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;">
      Wellbore Stability
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 21px;">
      The objective of the wellbore stability scheme is to determine the optimum mud weight window and/or wellbore trajectory in order to have a mechanically stable wellbore during and after drilling.
    </div>

    <div class="center" style="margin-top: 30px;">
