  <div id="hole_cleaning" style=" padding-top: 100px;">
    <p style="color: #d8e476; font-size: 28px; font-family: orgonboldregular; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;">
      Hole Cleaning
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 21px;">
      In a vertical section of the wellbore a modified Stokes' slip velocity model has been developed with the help of artificial neural networks. The outcome of the slip velocity model is the cuttings velocity and transportation ratio. In a deviated section, the concept of minimum transportation velocity (MTV) is utilized - or the minimum velocity to initiate the movement of the settled cuttings.
    </div>

    <div class="center" style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <%= image_tag "solutions/decision_support/hole_cleaning.png", style: "margin-top: 10px;" %>
    </div>
  </div>

