      Motor Stalls
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 21px;">
      The Corva platform uses a novel technique called edge detection to identify significant increases in standpipe and motor differential pressure, and significant decrease in instantaneous ROP. If all of these changes occur while the pump SPM is constant, then the motor stall detection algorithm is triggered.
    </div>

